:: \ invite {"position":"175,350","size":"100,100"}
//Says you, stranger! We haven't caught up in ages.//

She's right. You rarely speak anymore, mostly because you have been avoiding her. 

//Are you free now? Let's grab a bite.//

She reads the message immediately. You watch the three dots bobble up and down, and it makes you nervous.

//Sure. Where?//

You let out a breath you didn't know you were holding.


